          Browse Use Cases
        </a>
        <a
          href="/guides/ai-tools-for-beginners"
          class="link-soft font-sans font-normal text-sm"
        >
          Start as a beginner
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Most Popular -->
    <section class="section-pad border-t border-white/10">
      <h2 class="heading-2 mb-4 md:mb-5 text-center mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        Most Popular
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-6">
        <a
          href="/use-cases/best-ai-tools-for-marketing"
          class="card-soft hover:bg-slate-800/70 transition-colors block"
        >
          <h3 class="card-title mb-3">Best AI Tools for Marketing</h3>
          <p class="body-muted text-sm mb-4">
            Discover the top AI marketing tools to boost your campaigns, automate workflows, and drive better ROI.
