            Read more →
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What We Do -->
    <section class="section-pad max-w-4xl mx-auto border-t border-white/10">
      <h2 class="heading-2 mb-4 md:mb-5 text-center mx-auto">
        What We Do
      </h2>
      <p class="body-muted mb-6 mt-4 text-lg">
        PickMyAITools provides clear, practical guidance to help you choose AI tools that actually fit your needs. We focus on explaining what different types of AI tools do, who they're designed for, and how to match tools to your specific situation—whether you're a beginner, small business owner, freelancer, or professional looking to work more efficiently.
      </p>
      <p class="body-muted mb-6 text-lg">
        Our approach is straightforward: we explain what AI tools can realistically accomplish, help you understand which types of tools address your specific challenges, and provide guidance on choosing options that fit your experience level and budget. We don't recommend tools based on popularity or features—we focus on what actually helps you accomplish your goals.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Quick Links -->
    <section class="section-pad border-t border-white/10">
      <h2 class="heading-2 mb-4 md:mb-5 text-center mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        Quick Links
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-6">
        <div class="card-soft">
          <h3 class="card-title mb-4">Use Cases</h3>
          <p class="body-muted mb-6 text-sm">
            Find AI tools tailored to specific tasks like content writing, marketing, customer support, and more.
          </p>
          <a href="/use-cases" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-gray-100 font-sans text-sm transition-colors underline-offset-4 hover:underline inline-block">
            Explore Use Cases →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="card-soft">
