      <h2 class="heading-2 mb-4 md:mb-5">
        Ready to find your AI tool?
      </h2>
      <p class="body-muted mb-8">
        Start with our comprehensive guide to identify the right AI tool for your needs.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a
          href="/guides/which-ai-tool-should-i-use"
          class="btn-primary-soft font-sans font-normal text-sm"
        >
          Find My AI Tool
        </a>
        <a
          href="/guides/ai-tools-for-beginners"
          class="link-soft font-sans font-normal text-sm"
